@startuml

title USEI14 - Maximum Throughput (Max Flow)

skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

autonumber

actor OperationsAnalyst
participant System

OperationsAnalyst -> System: requestMaxFlowComputation()
activate System
    System --> OperationsAnalyst: displayMaxFlowUI()
deactivate System

OperationsAnalyst -> System: computeMaxFlow(sourceStation, sinkStation)
activate System
    System --> OperationsAnalyst: displayMaxFlowSummary(sourceId, targetId, maxFlowValue)
deactivate System

OperationsAnalyst -> System: requestAnalysisReport()
activate System
    System --> OperationsAnalyst: displayAnalysisReport(complexityAnalysis)
deactivate System

@enduml